  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nRelated to #921 \r\n\r\nWe currently depend on `ledgerco` which was a monolithic package that is now unmaintained. We should switch over to ledger's new packages hosted in their monorepo https://github.com/LedgerHQ/ledgerjs/tree/master/packages\r\n\r\nThis would also allow us to keep up to date with their packages, and handle transport layers much more easily (u2f vs nodehid), letting us implement hardware wallet signing for electron.\r\n\r\n",
