    "body": "Looks like we'll need to combine https://www.npmjs.com/package/@ledgerhq/hw-app-eth and https://www.npmjs.com/package/@ledgerhq/hw-transport-u2f to re-implement what we currently have, should be as simple as\r\n```\r\nimport ledgerU2F from '@ledgerhq/hw-transport-u2f';\r\nimport ledgerEth from '@ledgerhq/hw-app-eth';\r\n\r\nledgerU2F.create().then(transport => this.ethApp = new ledgerEth(transport));\r\n```",
